&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20250714" rel="nofollow"&gt;Mon, 14 Jul 2025 11:19:35 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
