&gt;&gt;&gt; the API in a non-backward-compatible way).
&gt;&gt;&gt; In &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/9452"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/9452&lt;/a&gt; there was 
