&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Safari fails many of these tests. Is that only due to the initial value 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; difference? Or are the mismatches here revealing other interoperability 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; issues?
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
