&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-4/#valdef-text-autospace-auto"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-4/#valdef-text-autospace-auto&lt;/a&gt;&gt;` 
&gt;&gt;&gt; value. This is a platform-specific value, but we can't simulate what iOS 
&gt;&gt;&gt; does.
