&gt;&gt; , Browser Bound Key as a tracking vector
&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://w3c.github.io/secure-payment-confirmation/#sctn-privacy-browser-bound-key-tracking-vector"&gt;https://w3c.github.io/secure-payment-confirmation/#sctn-privacy-browser-bound-key-tracking-vector&lt;/a&gt;&gt;.
