&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Thanks, filed &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/mozilla/standards-positions/issues/1143"&gt;https://github.com/mozilla/standards-positions/issues/1143&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;  and &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/435"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/435&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/435"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/435&lt;/a&gt;&gt;.
